item.title: By: Chris Blake
item.dc:creator: Chris Blake
item.description: I didn't realize until I bought the album on iTunes that the percussion in the beginning is somebody clicking their teeth. At least I think it is. The album is killer. Favorite new find since Egil Olsen. Everything is "best since something else" for me. I'm so petty.

item.title: By: Chris Blake

item.description: Holy hell, where have I been? I'm pretty sure this is the greatest pop song I have ever heard since Float On.
